OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMexico to spend $1.5bn on  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmodernising US border      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Mexico's President Andres Manuel Lopez 
OL,6, Obrador says his government will spend 
OL,7, $1.5bn (#1.26bn) on modernising his    
OL,8, country's border with the US.          
OL,10,FHe made the announcement after he met  
OL,11,FUS President Joe Biden at the White    
OL,12,FHouse.                                 
OL,14,FIn a joint statement, the Mexican      
OL,15,Fpresident called for a "bold programme"
OL,16,Fto deal with the record number of      
OL,17,Fmigrants crossing the US-Mexico border.
OL,19,FThe two men also said they would step  
OL,20,Fup the fight against drug trafficking. 
